Great British Menu - Series 10, Episodes 21 to 25




North East

Three newcomers - Mini Patel, Michael O'Hare and Tim Allen - are going head to head for a chance to represent the north east England region in the national finals. It's a battle for their four courses, and the chance to impress their formidable veteran chef.




Original Air Dates: 07-Sep-2015 to 11-Sep-2015
